{
    "description_long": "This is a small, walled graveyard featuring a stone chapel with a steep gabled roof and a bell tower. The graveyard is enclosed by a stone fence with pointed posts and an iron gate, and contains several upright headstones arranged in rows on a cobblestone path. A single leafless tree stands on a patch of bare earth, contrasting with the paved area where the graves are located. The chapel has arched windows and a prominent front entrance with steps leading up to it. The overall color palette is muted, with gray stone dominating the scene and brown earth providing contrast. The setting evokes a somber, historical atmosphere typical of older European cemeteries.",
    "description": "A walled graveyard with a stone chapel, several headstones, a leafless tree, and cobblestone paths. The scene is somber and dominated by gray stone and brown earth.",
